    <section>
      <title>erl_interface registry</title>
      <p>
	The <c>registry</c> functionality part of <c>erl_interface</c> was as of
	<seeguide marker="deprecations#otp-23">OTP 23 deprecated</seeguide>
	and was removed in OTP 24.
      </p>
