    <section>
       <title>Compilation of Latin-1 Encoded Erlang Files</title>
       <p>The Erlang compiler now refuses to compile source files
	encoded in Latin-1 without a <c>%% coding: latin-1</c> comment at the
	beginning of the file.</p>
    </section>
